data.description: Seller has agreed to add a 1st floor half bath!! installation week of 11/27/2023.  So 4 bedrooms and 1.5 baths. Welcome home to charming 605 Washington Street! This Roomy 4 Bedroom, Twin Home is the perfect balance of old school craftsmanship and modern upgrades. The  Covered Front Porch opens into the open Living and Dining room which boast hardwood floors, traditional moldings, high ceilings  and a wall of stylish ship lap. The Bright Kitchen shines with all newer stainless steel appliances, granite counter tops, a Walk In Pantry and Mud Room.  This home is move-in ready,  outfitted with up to date plumbing and electric, roof & replacement windows. It offers a use able Basement with tall ceilings and plenty of additional storage and workspace in the Basement. THE HUGE  detached 2 Car Garage with electric, rear 2 car  driveway parking. The exterior property affords outdoor living from the Covered Front Porch or Backyard Patio! Very Walk able location, Close to Schools, Shopping &  Bustling downtown area!
